<p style="margin-top:0;margin-right:0;margin-bottom:0;margin-left:28px;margin-bottom:0;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:20px">
    <span style="font-size:14px;font-family:&#39;微软雅黑&#39;,sans-serif;color:#464646">3.&nbsp;</span><span style="font-size:14px;font-family:&#39;微软雅黑&#39;,sans-serif;color:#464646">把编译原理上学的东西应用到编程中：如DFA,NFA，还有语法分析的各种方法等。</span>
</p>
